Package: surrogateTransportability
Type: Package
Title: Surrogate Inference via Random Probability Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements surrogate marker evaluation using random probability distributions
    to assess transportability across future studies. The method models future studies
    as draws from a mixture distribution combining the current study with innovation
    distributions, enabling inference about surrogate quality in new populations.
